rows.label: qst101202_msg002
rows.name:
I want you to find the
cause, mo. (Temp)

rows.label: qst101202_msg0002
rows.name:
The vegetables turned a
really bad color, mo...

rows.label: qst101202_msg0003
rows.name:
I took a bite, but it didn't
taste like food, mo!

rows.label: qst101202_msg0004
rows.name:
Umama's care was perfect. Your
fertilizer was perfect, too.

rows.label: qst101202_msg0005
rows.name:
That means the problem...
can only be the field, mo.

rows.label: qst101202_msg0006
rows.name:
Umama will investigate the soil,
so you look around the area to
see if there's a cause, mo.

rows.label: qst101202_msg0007
rows.name:
Please, mo... mo... My
tummy hurts, mo...

rows.label: qst101202_msg0101
rows.name:
I can tell if the soil is
good by tasting it, but...

rows.label: qst101202_msg0102
rows.name:
When I took one bite, I
saw my dead grandma, mo.

rows.label: qst101202_msg0103
rows.name:
Umama's field... It
might be ruined, mo...
